85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Gia-K%E1%BB%B7/Nh%E1%BA%A5t-ti%E1%BB%81n-h%C3%A0nh-t%E1%BA%B7ng-L%C3%A2m-M%E1%BA%ADu-Chi/poem-Snt1IqINeifyWFX8TNFYjw">Nhất tiền hành tặng Lâm Mậu Chi - 一錢行贈林戊之</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Gia-K%E1%BB%B7/author-WRSP543j56aeSlO4dZfsBQ">Ngô Gia Kỷ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Thanh-Chi%E1%BA%BFu/Than-ph%C3%A1-ho%C3%A1n-kh%C3%AA-sa/poem-x7uaTcWv4NUNkdhXlntSlA">Than phá hoán khê sa - 攤破浣溪沙</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Thanh-Chi%E1%BA%BFu/author-6q8syMJi1LKPt3rH8HfbQQ">Lý Thanh Chiếu</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tu%E1%BB%87-T%C4%A9nh-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/Thi%C3%AAn-hoa-ph%E1%BA%A5n/poem-ssUQmJ_JSiHgBhYi3PEGXQ">Thiên hoa phấn - 天花粉</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tu%E1%BB%87-T%C4%A9nh-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/author-9Mr6hsa5RsMoTXWLKUTJEg">Tuệ Tĩnh thiền sư</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
